services.name: line1 CONTENT
services.summary:
Drawing and painting flowers may seem like a first-year art student's assignment,

  • but Lorenzo Garcia brings depth, shadows, light, form and
  • color to new heights with his unique and
  • revolutionary technique of painting on canvas with ceramic glaze.
  • This session is sure to be a hit with mixed media buffs.
